or: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">三、系统生物学与生物网络</h3><ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 分子相互作用网络分析</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 系统生物学建模</li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 复杂生物系统模拟</li></ul><h3 id=\"9\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">四、生物医学计算应用</h3><ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left