; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">投稿建议</h2><ul style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 强调 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">算法创新或理论方法贡献</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 提供 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">真实生物数据集验证或实验分析</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 建议包含 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">统计显著性分析或严格模型评估</strong></li><li style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 在论文结构上保持 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">问题定义清晰、方法严谨、实验结果可复现</strong></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">投稿系统：https://mc.manuscriptcentral.com/tcbb</p><h2 id=\"5\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">期刊总结</h2>总体来看，<strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">IEEE Transactions on Computational Biology and Bioinformatics（TCBB）</strong> 是计算生物学与生物信息学领域具有稳定影响力的 IEEE Transactions 期刊之一。<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">凭借 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">计算方法与生命科学研究的交叉定位</strong>，该期刊长期汇聚 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">生物数据分析、算法模型与系统生物学研究</strong>等方向的重要成果。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">在计算生物学研究社区中，TCBB 仍然是 <strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">具有代表性的跨学科研究期刊平台之一</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">璇玑枢，我以渺小，与你同行——愿你的算法模型与生命数据洞见，在每一次计算中被更清晰地解析。</strong></p></section><p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/pdoYWlyPiaWE88Y687KoLpQPXSw646ISBHAUmLDZ1Hk9YxnuC551yF9ibpLiaLK4NyqNO15icJvZdsic5HqMUNJQwNg/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p>",
